# This project uses per-environment example files:
#
#   .env.local.example  — Local development (copy to .env.local)
#   .env.qa.example     — QA environment (set in AWS Amplify qa branch)
#   .env.prod.example   — Production environment (set in AWS Amplify main branch)
#
# Required variables in ALL environments:
#   DATABASE_URL          Neon PostgreSQL pooled connection
#   DIRECT_DATABASE_URL   Neon PostgreSQL direct connection (migrations)
#   AUTH_SECRET           NextAuth JWT secret (unique per environment)
#   NEXTAUTH_URL          Full URL of the deployed site
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_ENV       Environment name: "local" | "qa" | "prod"
